<![CDATA[<div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Dear </span>{!Service_Request__c.Contact_Name__c}<span style="font-size: 12pt;">,&nbsp;</span></font></div><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">We understand that the recent issue regarding "</span></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">{!Service_Request__c.Subject__c}"&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">is very important to you and I am working to get this resolved for you as quickly as possible. In order to track the issue and bring visibility to it at Honeywell I have logged a Service Request. (</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Service_Request__c.Name})</font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Let me know if you have any questions or concerns related to the service difficulty.&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thank you, we appreciate your business!</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Regards,</font></p><p class="HoneywellLetterBody" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Service_Request__c.OwnerName__c}</font></p><p class="HoneywellLetterBody" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Service_Request__c.Owner_Job_Title__c}</font></p><p class="HoneywellLetterBody" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Phone: &nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Service_Request__c.OwnerPhone}</font></p><p class="HoneywellLetterBody" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Email:&nbsp;</span></font>{!Service_Request__c.OwnerEmail}</font></p><p class="HoneywellLetterBody" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Service Request Number: {!Service_Request__c.Name}&nbsp;</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Service Request Subject: {!Service_Request__c.Subject__c}&nbsp;<br>Customer Account: {!Service_Request__c.Account_Name__c}<br>Customer Contact:&nbsp; {!Service_Request__c.Contact_Name__c}<br>Customer Phone :&nbsp; {!Service_Request__c.Primary_Work_Number__c}<br>Customer Email:{!Service_Request__c.Contact_Email__c}&nbsp;<br>Product Name:&nbsp; {!Service_Request__c.Product_Name__c}<br>Service Request Owner:&nbsp;{!Service_Request__c.OwnerName__c}</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Service Request Resolution Date:&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Service_Request__c.Customer_Due_Date__c}</span></font></p>]]></td>
